# TUG Autonomous Transport Robot
# Based on Aethon TUG form factor
# Boxy body with compartments, sensor dome on top
# Units: meters, total height ~1.3m

mtllib tug_robot.mtl

# ========================================
# PART 1: BASE PLATFORM (rounded rectangle)
# ========================================
o Base

# Bottom y=0.03, top y=0.10
# Roughly 0.5 wide (X) x 0.7 deep (Z)
v -0.25 0.03 -0.35
v  0.25 0.03 -0.35
v  0.25 0.03  0.35
v -0.25 0.03  0.35
v -0.25 0.10 -0.35
v  0.25 0.10 -0.35
v  0.25 0.10  0.35
v -0.25 0.10  0.35

usemtl Base_Dark
# Bottom
f 1 4 3 2
# Top
f 5 6 7 8
# Front
f 3 4 8 7
# Back
f 1 2 6 5
# Left
f 1 5 8 4
# Right
f 2 3 7 6

# ========================================
# PART 2: WHEELS (4 cylinders)
# ========================================
o Wheels

# Front-left wheel
